"kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GMenuModel"},{"type":"text","text":" represents the contents of a menu — an ordered list of"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"menu items. The items are associated with actions, which can be","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"activated through them. Items can be grouped in sections, and may","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"have submenus associated with them. Both items and sections usually","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"have some representation data, such as labels or icons. The type of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the associated action (ie whether it is stateful, and what kind of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"state it has) can influence the representation of the item."}]}}}